com.huawei.ipr.pof.manager.database

Class PMDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.huawei.ipr.pof.manager.database.PMDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPMDatabaseService, IFloodlightModule, IFloodlightService

    public class PMDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFloodlightModule, IPMDatabaseService
    SMDatabase implements IFloodlightModule and ISMDatabaseService.

    SMDatabase stores data and provides method interfaces to set and get.
    SMDatabase stores:

    • protocols
    • fields
    • packet types
    • data for each switches, stored in PMSwitchDatabase
    Author:
    Song Jian (jack.songjian@huawei.com), Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd.
